                    <h6 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center">
                        <i data-lucide="lightbulb" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-orange-600"></i>
                        管理建議
                    </h6>
                    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 p-4 rounded-lg">
